data.description: Offering 10K in CCA!!!  Beautiful, 4 bedroom 2 1/2 bath home on corner lot of a quiet cul-de-sac.  Large living spaces and generous sized bedrooms, this house offers all the features that modern construction (2019) has to offer. An open concept kitchen featuring stainless appliances, granite, a pantry and convenient center island for extra counter space with bar seating. The dining room and living room are spacious and offer lots of versatility to utilize the space to best serve your needs.  The LVP flooring provides easy maintenance throughout the first floor.  Upstairs is the primary bedroom featuring a walk-in closet and private bath with duel sinks, also three additional bedrooms, the hall bathroom with 2 sinks and the handy laundry room. Outside is a fully fenced in backyard with a patio for all your entertaining needs. Parking includes a one-car attached garage and driveway space for 2 cars. Near to easy interstate access, area military bases, shipyards, shopping, & restaurants.
